VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=262e04be-db83-4761-8a0e-31fad3d64adb

# --- Build & deploy ---
# Local: copy this file to .env and set VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY, then: npm run build
# Vercel: Project Settings → Environment Variables → VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY (Production, Preview, Development)
# 2. Upload the entire dist/ folder (index.html + assets/ together).
# 3. SPA refresh: upload dist/.htaccess + dist/404.html + index.html (Hostinger).
#    Vercel: vercel.json rewrites are included at repo root.

# Optional: full Google Maps embed URL (overrides address-based map on the contact page)
# VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_EMBED_URL=https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=...

# - Email support@web3forms.com with your live URL to approve the domain.
# - If using Pro "Restrict to Domain", add every hostname you use (with and without www).
